{"tid":539762,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴辛迪卡索拉望下季復出 坦言「可能已經唔識踢波」","createTime":"2018-01-25T00:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T07:54:46.000Z","uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5814a58a2d609370beb5259d88ee6d146a4e42","tid":539762,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:21:52.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴中場辛迪卡索拉自前年因為左足踝受傷後，已年多未有復出。早前他向傳媒表示，希望下個球季能夠復出，但他坦言自己可能已經不懂如何踢足球，令人心酸。<br />\n<br />\n辛迪卡索拉接受英國傳媒訪問，話自己曾經有多次掛靴嘅念頭，亦有不少人勸他不要繼續，「或者我復出的時候，已經不懂踢足球，但我會努力投入訓練，希望可以在高水平賽事中再出場」辛迪卡索拉亦指自己未來可能會回到西班牙，亦可能從事執教工作。<br />\n<br />\n辛迪卡索拉自受傷後，已接受10次手術，早前更因傷口感染，可能需要截肢。現在左足踝肌腱已被減少8厘米之多，而且由於皮膚不足，要將手部的皮膚移植到右腳，包括部份有愛女名字紋身的位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39bf7a93df3499ca86d40cbcbcae40226b9c3006","tid":539762,"uid":4586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:24:55.000Z","msg":"Get well soon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1d7e1e2d2c89aa3a3c8f85d67eaad238f196fb","tid":539762,"uid":4957,"like":7,"dislike":63,"score":-56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:28:16.000Z","msg":"攔啦 阿仙奴己經唔再需要你"},{"pid":"a6d69750cc67118cb80bc76ee6a2bcad8a76f50b","tid":539762,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:28:53.000Z","msg":"年年都咁講嫁啦 到時咪又傷"},{"pid":"d41e5b24582d4e45c10c9528b1d5b9a13a1269a2","tid":539762,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377de35706da216b7db1ac6dfc4977a457499f4c","tid":539762,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2619c124e746c62b38a3623586ea15b0